      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>These records concern lands in Stafford County and Lee
         County, Virginia and Winston County, Mississippi. There is
         also a pardon issued by President Andrew Johnson to John C.
         Shelton of Stafford County.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      <arrangement>
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>Items are arranged chronologically.</p>
      </arrangement>
